nodes.text: Dipika O'Neill Joti (born 1967) is an Indian actress best known to have portrayed Depa Billaba in Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace. Footage of Billaba and other Jedi High Council members from that film was reused for Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones, although Joti filmed no new footage for the second installment.
